content.problemStatement:
Which of the following Java code snippets correctly defines a main method with a code block?

Option 1:
```java
public static void main(String[] args)
    System.out.println("Hello!");
```

Option 2:
```java
public static void main(String[] args) {
    System.out.println("Hello!");
}
```

Option 3:
```java
public static void main(String[] args) (
    System.out.println("Hello!");
)
```

Option 4:
```java
public static void main(String[] args) []
    System.out.println("Hello!");
```

